#. HTML: <section id="vagga"><section class="sutta" data-uid="an1.268" id="268"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an1.268-277:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 1 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 1 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an1.268-277:0.2"
msgid "21. Paṭhamavagga "
msgstr "21. First "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an1.268-277:0.3"
msgid "268 "
msgstr "268 "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli1.27, sc268.1
#. VAR: kañci → kiñci (mr)
msgctxt "an1.268-277:268.1.1"
msgid "“Aṭṭhānametaṃ, bhikkhave, anavakāso yaṃ diṭṭhisampanno puggalo kañci saṅkhāraṃ niccato upagaccheyya. Netaṃ ṭhānaṃ vijjati. "
msgstr "“It is impossible, mendicants, it cannot happen for a person accomplished in view to take any condition as permanent. That is not possible. "

msgctxt "an1.268-277:268.1.2"
msgid "Ṭhānañca kho etaṃ, bhikkhave, vijjati yaṃ puthujjano kañci saṅkhāraṃ niccato upagaccheyya. Ṭhānametaṃ vijjatī”ti. "
msgstr "But it is possible for an ordinary person to take some condition as permanent. That is possible.” "

#. HTML: </p></article></section><section class="sutta" data-uid="an1.269" id="269"><article><div class="hgroup"><h1>
msgctxt "an1.268-277:268.1.3"
msgid "269 "
msgstr "269 "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc269.1
msgctxt "an1.268-277:269.1.1"
msgid "“Aṭṭhānametaṃ, bhikkhave, anavakāso yaṃ diṭṭhisampanno puggalo kañci saṅkhāraṃ sukhato upagaccheyya. Netaṃ ṭhānaṃ vijjati. "
msgstr "“It is impossible, mendicants, it cannot happen for a person accomplished in view to take any condition as pleasant. "

msgctxt "an1.268-277:269.1.2"
msgid "Ṭhānañca kho etaṃ, bhikkhave, vijjati yaṃ puthujjano kañci saṅkhāraṃ sukhato upagaccheyya. Ṭhānametaṃ vijjatī”ti. "
msgstr "But it is possible for an ordinary person to take some condition as pleasant.” "

#. HTML: </p></article></section><section class="sutta" data-uid="an1.270" id="270"><article><div class="hgroup"><h1>
msgctxt "an1.268-277:269.1.3"
msgid "270 "
msgstr "270 "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc270.1
msgctxt "an1.268-277:270.1.1"
msgid "“Aṭṭhānametaṃ, bhikkhave, anavakāso yaṃ diṭṭhisampanno puggalo kañci dhammaṃ attato upagaccheyya. Netaṃ ṭhānaṃ vijjati. "
msgstr "“It is impossible, mendicants, it cannot happen for a person accomplished in view to take anything as self. "

msgctxt "an1.268-277:270.1.2"
msgid "Ṭhānañca kho etaṃ, bhikkhave, vijjati yaṃ puthujjano kañci dhammaṃ attato upagaccheyya. Ṭhānametaṃ vijjatī”ti. "
msgstr "But it is possible for an ordinary person to take something as self.” "

#. HTML: </p></article></section><section class="sutta" data-uid="an1.271" id="271"><article><div class="hgroup"><h1>
msgctxt "an1.268-277:270.1.3"
msgid "271 "
msgstr "271 "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc271.1
msgctxt "an1.268-277:271.1.1"
msgid "“Aṭṭhānametaṃ, bhikkhave, anavakāso yaṃ diṭṭhisampanno puggalo mātaraṃ jīvitā voropeyya. Netaṃ ṭhānaṃ vijjati. "
msgstr "“It is impossible, mendicants, it cannot happen for a person accomplished in view to murder their mother. "

msgctxt "an1.268-277:271.1.2"
msgid "Ṭhānañca kho, bhikkhave, vijjati yaṃ puthujjano mātaraṃ jīvitā voropeyya. Ṭhānametaṃ vijjatī”ti. "
msgstr "But it is possible for an ordinary person to murder their mother.” "

#. HTML: </p></article></section><section class="sutta" data-uid="an1.272" id="272"><article><div class="hgroup"><h1>
msgctxt "an1.268-277:271.1.3"
msgid "272 "
msgstr "272 "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc272.1
msgctxt "an1.268-277:272.1.1"
msgid "“Aṭṭhānametaṃ, bhikkhave, anavakāso yaṃ diṭṭhisampanno puggalo pitaraṃ jīvitā voropeyya. Netaṃ ṭhānaṃ vijjati. "
msgstr "“It is impossible, mendicants, it cannot happen for a person accomplished in view to murder their father. "

msgctxt "an1.268-277:272.1.2"
msgid "Ṭhānañca kho etaṃ, bhikkhave, vijjati yaṃ puthujjano pitaraṃ jīvitā voropeyya. Ṭhānametaṃ vijjatī”ti. "
msgstr "But it is possible for an ordinary person to murder their father.” "

#. HTML: </p></article></section><section class="sutta" data-uid="an1.273" id="273"><article><div class="hgroup"><h1>
msgctxt "an1.268-277:272.1.3"
msgid "273 "
msgstr "273 "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc273.1
msgctxt "an1.268-277:273.1.1"
msgid "“Aṭṭhānametaṃ, bhikkhave, anavakāso yaṃ diṭṭhisampanno puggalo arahantaṃ jīvitā voropeyya. Netaṃ ṭhānaṃ vijjati. "
msgstr "“It is impossible, mendicants, it cannot happen for a person accomplished in view to murder a perfected one. "

msgctxt "an1.268-277:273.1.2"
msgid "Ṭhānañca kho etaṃ, bhikkhave, vijjati yaṃ puthujjano arahantaṃ jīvitā voropeyya. Ṭhānametaṃ vijjatī”ti. "
msgstr "But it is possible for an ordinary person to murder a perfected one.” "

#. HTML: </p></article></section><section class="sutta" data-uid="an1.274" id="274"><article><div class="hgroup"><h1>
msgctxt "an1.268-277:273.1.3"
msgid "274 "
msgstr "274 "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc274.1
msgctxt "an1.268-277:274.1.1"
msgid "“Aṭṭhānametaṃ, bhikkhave, anavakāso yaṃ diṭṭhisampanno puggalo tathāgatassa paduṭṭhacitto lohitaṃ uppādeyya. Netaṃ ṭhānaṃ vijjati. "
msgstr "“It is impossible, mendicants, it cannot happen for a person accomplished in view to injure a Realized One with malicious intent. "

msgctxt "an1.268-277:274.1.2"
msgid "Ṭhānañca kho etaṃ, bhikkhave, vijjati yaṃ puthujjano tathāgatassa paduṭṭhacitto lohitaṃ uppādeyya. Ṭhānametaṃ vijjatī”ti. "
msgstr "But it is possible for an ordinary person to injure a Realized One with malicious intent.” "

#. HTML: </p></article></section><section class="sutta" data-uid="an1.275" id="275"><article><div class="hgroup"><h1>
msgctxt "an1.268-277:274.1.3"
msgid "275 "
msgstr "275 "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc275.1
msgctxt "an1.268-277:275.1.1"
msgid "“Aṭṭhānametaṃ, bhikkhave, anavakāso yaṃ diṭṭhisampanno puggalo saṅghaṃ bhindeyya. Netaṃ ṭhānaṃ vijjati. "
msgstr "“It is impossible, mendicants, it cannot happen for a person accomplished in view to cause a schism in the Saṅgha. "

msgctxt "an1.268-277:275.1.2"
msgid "Ṭhānañca kho etaṃ, bhikkhave, vijjati yaṃ puthujjano saṅghaṃ bhindeyya. Ṭhānametaṃ vijjatī”ti. "
msgstr "But it is possible for an ordinary person to cause a schism in the Saṅgha.” "

#. HTML: </p></article></section><section class="sutta" data-uid="an1.276" id="276"><article><div class="hgroup"><h1>
msgctxt "an1.268-277:275.1.3"
msgid "276 "
msgstr "276 "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc276.1
msgctxt "an1.268-277:276.1.1"
msgid "“Aṭṭhānametaṃ, bhikkhave, anavakāso yaṃ diṭṭhisampanno puggalo aññaṃ satthāraṃ uddiseyya. Netaṃ ṭhānaṃ vijjati. "
msgstr "“It is impossible, mendicants, it cannot happen for a person accomplished in view to acknowledge another teacher. "

msgctxt "an1.268-277:276.1.2"
msgid "Ṭhānañca kho etaṃ, bhikkhave, vijjati yaṃ puthujjano aññaṃ satthāraṃ uddiseyya. Ṭhānametaṃ vijjatī”ti. "
msgstr "But it is possible for an ordinary person to acknowledge another teacher.” "

#. HTML: </p></article></section><section class="sutta" data-uid="an1.277" id="277"><article><div class="hgroup"><h1>
msgctxt "an1.268-277:276.1.3"
msgid "277 "
msgstr "277 "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli1.28, sc277.1
msgctxt "an1.268-277:277.1.1"
msgid "“Aṭṭhānametaṃ, bhikkhave, anavakāso yaṃ ekissā lokadhātuyā dve arahanto sammāsambuddhā apubbaṃ acarimaṃ uppajjeyyuṃ. Netaṃ ṭhānaṃ vijjati. "
msgstr "“It is impossible, mendicants, it cannot happen for two perfected ones, fully awakened Buddhas to arise in the same solar system at the same time. "

msgctxt "an1.268-277:277.1.2"
msgid "Ṭhānañca kho etaṃ, bhikkhave, vijjati yaṃ ekissā lokadhātuyā ekova arahaṃ sammāsambuddho uppajjeyya. Ṭhānametaṃ vijjatī”ti. "
msgstr "But it is possible for just one perfected one, a fully awakened Buddha, to arise in one solar system.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an1.268-277:277.1.3"
msgid "Vaggo paṭhamo. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></section></body></html>
